        <LivingArrangementsWithoutChildren factor="1.03269">
            <!--
            There were about 11 624 000 households in 2021 in germany with at least 1 parent and at least 1 child
            (type of households, that were generated in phase 1).
            There were about 12 004 000 households in 2021 in germany with couples, that had no child
            (type of household, that must be generated in phase 2).
            The amount of households, that are now generated in phase 2 depends on the amount of households that were
            generated during phase 1.
            factor = (12 004) / (11 624) = 1.03269

            Source:
            https://www.destatis.de/DE/Themen/Gesellschaft-Umwelt/Bevoelkerung/Haushalte-Familien/Publikationen/Downloads-Haushalte/haushalte-familien-2010300217004.html
            table: 3.1.0


